      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_341gc' title='Col. 341GC &mdash; HL Deb 04 February 2004 vol 656 c341GC' name='column_341gc' href='#column_341gc' rel='bookmark'>341GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-04173'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040204_GCR_3' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
