        Clause 78 [<span class="italic">Application of civil law to renewable energy instalknions etc</span>.]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-04183'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040204_GCR_13' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
