        <q>Page 61, line 22, leave out subsections (4) and (5).</q>
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_342gc' title='Col. 342GC &mdash; HL Deb 04 February 2004 vol 656 c342GC' name='column_342gc' href='#column_342gc' rel='bookmark'>342GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-04184'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040204_GCR_14' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The noble Lord said: In moving Amendment No. 106EC, I shall speak also to the other government amendments in the group. It may be&#x2014;
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-04185'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040204_GCR_15'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-doreen-miller' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
