          <p class='first-para'>
            I am sorry, I did not hear the answer about when the cable is under water.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-04351'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040204_GCR_181'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-whitty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
